                                                   <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If prescriptive, For parent CF1R-NCB If M03_WaterHeatingSystemOption == OptionSingleHWH (display term "1") And # of bedrooms LTE 1 let user pick from list of HPWH in B2hp03_HeatPumpWaterHeaterModel End If; 
