Else If M03_WaterHeatingSystemOption == OptionTier3SingleHWH (display term "2") user can select a Tier 3 or higher heat pump water heater from  the entire list of Tier 3 heat pump water heaters in B2hp03_HeatPumpWaterHeatersTier3NEEA OR from any simulation group of  Tier 3 or higher water heaters End If </xs:documentation>
                                                   
                                                
